*xmms-alsa-1.2.10-r3 (27 May 2005)

  27 May 2005; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  +xmms-alsa-1.2.10-r3.ebuild:
  Bump to include various bugfixes included upstream. Removes mmap and
  single-thread modes as the new threaded mode from tiwai is much better.
  Cleans up configure window.

  22 May 2005; Guy Martin <gmsoft@gentoo.org> xmms-alsa-1.2.10-r2.ebuild:
  Stable on hppa.

  11 May 2005; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  xmms-alsa-1.2.10-r2.ebuild:
  Stable amd64, sparc, x86.

